{"tid":882419,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬列斯痛緬維猜：就像我父親","createTime":"2018-10-30T06:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T12:05:11.000Z","uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6eab7d066f625c08c2522519c142a2995653f149","tid":882419,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=iDK3FfCBOU4dQZObA9%2Fo6VzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=ca674c25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】為曼城對熱刺攻入奠勝球的馬列斯，直言以手指向天之舉是把入球獻舊班主維猜，並指對方猶如自己的父親，為其離世非常傷痛。<br />\n<br />\n前李斯特城鋒將馬列斯（Riyad Mahrez）賽後接受天空體育訪問時，直指在李城班主維猜意外離世後，這夜作賽時感到艱難。「這對我而言是非常、非常艱難，遇上這種事很難過，老闆（維猜）對我是十分特別，我在那兒度過了4年半，與他滿有回憶。他實在是一個好人。」<br />\n<br />\n「我非常、非常傷痛，這解釋為何當我入球後，為了他手指向天，他為我及李斯特城做了很多，這委實非常傷痛。」馬列斯顯得傷感：「他就像我父親，他很特別。這是艱難的狀況，我與李斯特城及遇難者的家人同在。」<br />\n<br />\n這位阿爾及利亞翼鋒近3次鬥熱刺參與了5個入球（3入球2助攻），不可不說成熱刺的剋星。"},{"pid":"1d465f3c3d2e6e2013e3d0bead9697efcf0f4245","tid":882419,"uid":47268,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"夠你嗰日射失12碼傷痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b61914ce36ef44bd685974a3c35292152a5f3d3","tid":882419,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"我都想維猜係我父親<br />\n<br />\n啲遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d571297097a9f37c8d6ce687e75641fecb4034","tid":882419,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"馬列斯：Allahu Akbar"},{"pid":"56576ab0594c283b7a583b14c30d3c06fbb0fc32","tid":882419,"uid":166413,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"係老豆就唔會成日嗌走喇25仔"},{"pi